Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.22,0:00:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,《法外情真》前情回顾\N{\fs12}Previously on The Guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.44,0:00:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他们给了我你的工作\N{\fs12}I been offered your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我接受了\N{\fs12}I took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,露露跟我说  你辞职了\N{\fs12}Lulu told me that you... that you quit.
