Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.36,0:00:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,今早跟维多利亚求婚了\N{\fs12}Proposed to Victoria this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,还有  我快死了\N{\fs12}And, I'm dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
