Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.48,0:00:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,卢伽雷氏症\N{\fs12}Lou Gehrig's disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这已经是我们两天里第三次约会了  杰克\N{\fs12}Look, this is our third date in two days, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我还一点儿都不了解你呢\N{\fs12}I don't really know anything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.72,0:00:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我不是同性恋\N{\fs12}Look I'm not gay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.66,0:00:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不是男女之间的事儿\N{\fs12}It's not romantic or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想加入乡村俱乐部而已\N{\fs12}I just wanted to join the country club...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的很喜欢那种  能和凯特这样的人在一起的想法\N{\fs12}I really like the idea of being with someone like Kate...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.46,0:00:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克·发林  这是艾米莉·伯恩斯利\N{\fs12}Nike Fallin, this is Emily Bernsley.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.46,0:00:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我  呃  今天给威廉姆·科特打电话了\N{\fs12}I, uh, called William Kurt today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他说她上周把她辞退了\N{\fs12}And he said he fired her last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.08,0:00:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的很喜欢你们所作的事\N{\fs12}I really like what you guys do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不希望你走  - 就因为我生病了吗\N{\fs12}- I don't want you to go. - Because I'm sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,因为\N{\fs12}Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.62,0:00:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你无可替代\N{\fs12}You are indispensable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.62,0:00:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克\N{\fs12}So Nick...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.70,0:00:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想\N{\fs12}I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我能往西游多远\N{\fs12}of seeing how far west I could swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.32,0:00:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我快要死了  尼克\N{\fs12}I am going to die, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.68,0:00:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我努力不去想这件事  你知道吗\N{\fs12}I'm trying to get my mind around it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  你把这个给忘了\N{\fs12}Honey, you forgot this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.71,0:01:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没有你我该怎么办  - 我知道\N{\fs12}- What would I do without you? - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 照顾好自己  - 再见亲爱的\N{\fs12}- Take care. - Bye, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  请问需要什么帮助\N{\fs12}Hello. Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,另外  看起来去皮特隧道的一条路\N{\fs12}And it looks like one of the lanes of the ft. Pitt Tunnel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,关闭了\N{\fs12}inbound is closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所以可以的话  请绕行西区大桥\N{\fs12}So you might want to take the West End Bridge if you possibly can.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.22,0:01:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,再来看看这条新闻  又一起枪击\N{\fs12}Now checking the news.Another shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这次是在南部的一个安静郊区\N{\fs12}This time in a quiet suburb south of the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚我要不要穿我的新衬衣呢\N{\fs12}So shall I wear my new shirt tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你的紫色新衬衣  - 是薰衣草色的\N{\fs12}- Your new purple shirt? - It's lavender.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.11,0:02:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fs12}no.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.53,0:02:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天晚上不应该穿你的紫色新衬衣\N{\fs12}You should not wear your new purple shirt tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不应该吗\N{\fs12}No?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.59,0:02:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你不喜欢我的薰衣草色衬衫  是吗\N{\fs12}You don't like my lavender shirt, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.79,0:02:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢七十岁以上的女人穿紫色的\N{\fs12}I like purple on women over the age of 70.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想这样吗\N{\fs12}You don't want to do this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,参加你的新成员晚宴吗\N{\fs12}Attend your new members' dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  说不定你走运  可能他们会取消之类的\N{\fs12}Well, maybe you'll get lucky. Maybe they'll cancel it or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他们为什么这么做\N{\fs12}Why would they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这个  城里有个家伙瞎转悠  冷血的枪杀别人\N{\fs12}Well, there's some guy running around the city shooting people in cold blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.94,0:02:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人的悲剧并没有阻止新教徒集会\N{\fs12}Other people's tragedies don't prohibit the WASPs from gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.55,0:02:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上  这只会鼓励他们\N{\fs12}ln fact, it only encourages them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我加入你爸爸的俱乐部  这确实很影响你  是吗\N{\fs12}It really bothers you that I'm joining your father's club, doesn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:03:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,黑色鞋子配这个  不要棕色的\N{\fs12}Black shoes with this, not brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好  有邮件吗\N{\fs12}Morning. Mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这是地区检察官的传票\N{\fs12}This is a subpoena from the District Attorney's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 尼克  你有空吗  - 当然\N{\fs12}- Uh, Nick, you have a second? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还需要一些客户表格\N{\fs12}We're gonna need some more client forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你那个课程上的怎么样  - 哪个课程\N{\fs12}- How are you doing with that course? - What course?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你和维多利亚一起做的那个课程  - 应对肌萎缩性侧索硬化症\N{\fs12}- The course you're doing with Victoria? - Coping with ALS?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的  - 非常有趣  非常有娱乐性\N{\fs12}- Yeah. - Very fun. Very entertaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不错\N{\fs12}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,几天前我们了解到  在不久的将来\N{\fs12}A few days ago we learned that at a certain point in the not-too-distant future,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须用眉毛去交流\N{\fs12}I would have to use my eyebrows to communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,所以维多利亚很崩溃  我们取消了订婚\N{\fs12}So...Victoria has a major meltdown. We kinda break om the engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文\N{\fs12}Alvin...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,劳里有一个有意思案例给你\N{\fs12}Laurie's got an interesting case for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子的名字叫安德鲁·福特\N{\fs12}Child's name is Andrew Ford.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,十天前他在他的卧室被袭击了\N{\fs12}Ten days ago, he was attacked in his bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他被猥亵然后被刺伤了\N{\fs12}He was molested and then stabbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,警方觉得他爸爸是袭击者\N{\fs12}The police think that the father was the attacker
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,所以社会服务想让把他从家中带走\N{\fs12}so Social Services wants to remove him from his home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他爸爸曾经被捕过吗  - 是的  但是他被保释了\N{\fs12}- Has the father been arrested? - Yes, but he's out on bail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,劳里现在掌握了全部的细节\N{\fs12}Laurie's, getting all the details right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  阿尔文  我对维多利亚的事情表示抱歉\N{\fs12}Listen, Alvin, I'm sorry about Victoria.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的 如果有任何事情我能做的\N{\fs12}You know, if there's anything I can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,劳里会帮你了解情况的\N{\fs12}Laurie will bring you up to speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你都了解些什么\N{\fs12}What do you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他爸爸的一件T恤在安德鲁的房间里被发现  上面还有精液\N{\fs12}One of his father's T-shirts was found in Andrew's room with semen stains on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.19,0:05:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就在攻击发生的几个小时前\N{\fs12}And just a few hours before the attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他爸爸从网站上下载了色情图片\N{\fs12}his father downloaded pornographic images from the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.73,0:05:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 儿童色情图吗  - 不是\N{\fs12}- Child porn? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.68,0:05:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  这个看起来不足以与父亲有关\N{\fs12}Well, it doesn't seem enough to implicate the father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没有任何强行进入的痕迹\N{\fs12}There were no signs of forced entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,福特先生和福特太太不再共用一个卧室  所以他没有不在场证明\N{\fs12}Mr. and Mrs. Ford no longer share a bedroom, so he doesn't have an alibi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,而且福特先生拒绝警方对安德鲁进行\N{\fs12}and Mr. Ford refused to allow the police to conduct
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,性侵检查\N{\fs12}a sexual assault exam on Andrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那  那孩子说了什么\N{\fs12}What's the-- what's the kid saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他进医院的时候  他告诉警方\N{\fs12}When he was in the hospital, he told the police
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,袭击他的人一直再重复  不要再说了\N{\fs12}his attacker kept repeating ''Don't tell anyone.''
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但是警方问他能否去指认袭击他的人  他说不要\N{\fs12}But when the police asked him if he could identify his attacker, he said, ''No.''
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他说他什么都不记得了\N{\fs12}And now he says he doesn't remember anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么想\N{\fs12}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,安德鲁的前臂和手指都有防御性伤口\N{\fs12}Andrew has defensive wounds on his forearm and his fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我想他可能看见是谁对他做了这些\N{\fs12}So I think he probably saw who did this to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:05:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,安德鲁  这是尼克·法林\N{\fs12}Hey, Andrew. This is Nick Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs12}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么样\N{\fs12}How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须向法院建议你应该住哪\N{\fs12}I have to make a recommendation to the court about where you should live
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,直到警方把这件事情解决\N{\fs12}while the police are sorting this thing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.41,0:06:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我有些问题必须要问你\N{\fs12}So I have to ask you a few questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想回家\N{\fs12}I just want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  我理解你\N{\fs12}Right. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你和你爸爸住在一起你不担心吗\N{\fs12}You're not concerned about living with your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的想不起来发生了什么\N{\fs12}I really can't remember what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有撒谎\N{\fs12}I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的想不起来了\N{\fs12}I really can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  艾米丽  你确定你不想这个工作吗\N{\fs12}Well, Emily, are you sure you don't want the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  但是不用了\N{\fs12}Thank you for the offer, but no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不呢\N{\fs12}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这个组织正和我看到的一样  注定要失败的\N{\fs12}The organization is, as I see it, kind of... it's set up to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文·马斯特森生病了\N{\fs12}Alvin Masterson is ill with--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:07:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的好的  - 而且你缺少律师\N{\fs12}- Right. Right. - And you're short of attorneys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你的志愿者的项目  留住尼克  基本上不存在\N{\fs12}And your volunteer program, save for that Nick guy, it's basically non-existent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你马上要有个宝宝了  所以\N{\fs12}You're gonna have a baby soon, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这个组织  它就注定\N{\fs12}The organization, it's set up to--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你为了一个原因来这里  是吗\N{\fs12}You came here for a reason, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.25,0:07:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得  看吧  我不知道为什么柯克&麦吉律所会解雇你\N{\fs12}I mean, look, I don't know why you got fired from Kirk & McGee,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但是告诉你实话  这很有可能是我雇你的原因\N{\fs12}but to tell you the truth, it's probably why I want to hire you.
