Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我现在没有时间放在这事上\N{\fs12}Uh, no, I don't have time for that right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那些表格帮我找好了吗吗  谢谢\N{\fs12}Do you have those forms for me? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子那边情况怎么样\N{\fs12}How did it go with the kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  他说他不记得了  而且他只想回家\N{\fs12}Well, he says he doesn't remember, and, uh, he wants to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文  我们已经被传唤出庭听证会了\N{\fs12}Alvin, we've been subpoenaed to appear at a hearing to show cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs12}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,地方检察官想要看我们一些客户的文件客户的\N{\fs12}The DA wants to see some of our clients' files.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来\N{\fs12}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 尼克  - 怎么了\N{\fs12}- Nick? - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 艾米丽  - 是啊我记得\N{\fs12}- Emily. - Yeah, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说福特的案子了  我想我可能能帮到你\N{\fs12}I heard about the Ford case, and I was wondering if I might help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 帮我  - 是啊\N{\fs12}- Help me? - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果你需要帮助的话我很乐意  - 不用了谢谢\N{\fs12}-lf you need some help, I'd like to- - No. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,很感谢  但是我现在还能应付的过来\N{\fs12}I appreciate it, but I can handle it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.86,0:08:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,传票上面说他们想知道在1985年6月到12月之间\N{\fs12}It says in the subpoena that they want the names of any clients
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,被安置到白橡树集体之家\N{\fs12}who were placed in the White Oak group home
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.76,0:08:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,所有客户的名单\N{\fs12}between June and December of 1985.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,白橡树  我从来没听说过\N{\fs12}White Oak? I've never heard of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.83,0:08:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为他们十年就被关掉了\N{\fs12}That's because they were shut down ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  但那之前他们是做什么的呢\N{\fs12}Yeah, but what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,遭受性虐待的男孩的治疗中心\N{\fs12}A treatment center for sexually abused boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么警方想要这些记录\N{\fs12}And why are the police seeking the records?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,传票上没说  但是我们不可能把这些交给他们\N{\fs12}It doesn't say. But there's no way that we're handing them over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这些孩子相信我们  露露  他们相信我们会照顾他们\N{\fs12}These kids trusted us, Lulu. They trusted us to look after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好卡尔  - 你好杰克\N{\fs12}- Hi, Carl. - Hey, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,给我来些薄荷糖  还有  呃\N{\fs12}I'll get those mints. And, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:08:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你只有这些花了吗\N{\fs12}These the only flowers you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,什么  这些对你的秘书还不够\N{\fs12}What, they're not good enough for your secretary?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这些不是给我秘书的  - 不错嘛\N{\fs12}- Oh, these aren't for my secretary. - Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能会  呃  要这些薰衣草\N{\fs12}Maybe I'll, uh, get the lavender ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克  如果一个女孩子真的喜欢你  别从我这儿买\N{\fs12}Jake, If a girl actually likes you, don't buy flowers from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,去好的地方买\N{\fs12}Go someplace good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这一刀买薄荷糖\N{\fs12}That's a dollar for the mints.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢了卡尔\N{\fs12}Thanks, Carl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,法官大人  这些记录受到律师与客户之间的保密协议保护\N{\fs12}Your Honor, these records are protected by attorney/client confidentially.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,此外  这些记录是密封的\N{\fs12}Furthermore, these records are sealed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们有关未成年人的性虐待\N{\fs12}because they concern the sexual abuse of minors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,马斯特森先生  让芬纳兰先生解释\N{\fs12}Mr. Masterson, allow Mr. Finneran to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,法官大人  您的传票1985年6月到12月之间住在白橡树之家的人\N{\fs12}Your Honor, our subpoena requests information regarding those LSP clients
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有关这些LSP客户端的信息\N{\fs12}who lived in the White Oak group home between June and December of 1985.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么警察对这些人感兴趣\N{\fs12}Why are the police interested in these residents?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这有点复杂\N{\fs12}This is somewhat complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  尽你所能解释清楚\N{\fs12}Well, then do your best to be clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.82,0:09:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那些最近被谋杀的男性  都被指控为恋童癖\N{\fs12}Those men who were recently murdered are accused pedophiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,据说每个人都虐待了儿童\N{\fs12}Each had allegedly abused children in their care.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在说这些恋童癖住在同一个集体家庭里吗\N{\fs12}And you're saying these pedophiles lived together in a group home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不  当然不是了  法官大人  不是\N{\fs12}No. No, no. Of course not, Your Honor, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这些受害者19年前都住在\N{\fs12}The victims lived together in the White Oak group home,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,白橡树之家里\N{\fs12}19 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这个让你感兴趣\N{\fs12}Why does this interest you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,根据警探所说  一个曾住在白橡树的居民记得\N{\fs12}According to detectives, one of the former White Oak residents
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,另外一个人  不停的幻想\N{\fs12}remembers another one fantasizing, repeatedly
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,找到并杀了那些侵犯他们的人\N{\fs12}about hunting down and killing their abusers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哪一个  - 问题就在这儿\N{\fs12}- Which one? - Well, this is our problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的目击者不记得名字  何况事情是在20年前\N{\fs12}Our witness can't remember the name. It was, after all, 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.82,0:10:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,马斯特森先生  作为儿童拥护者\N{\fs12}Mr. Masterson, as a child advocate,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,您是否需要就最利于你客户的方案行事\N{\fs12}aren't you required to act in your clients' best interests?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候会需要您泄露机密信息吗\N{\fs12}And doesn't that sometimes require you to reveal confidential information?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这没错  法官大人  但是我没看到这种情况有什么影响\N{\fs12}Well, that's true, Your Honor, but I fail to see how this situation has any bearing--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,马斯特森先生  我要求您提供这些文件\N{\fs12}Mr. Masterson, I'm ordering you to produce these files.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢您  法官大人  - 但是不是向芬纳兰先生提供\N{\fs12}- Thank you, Your Honor. - But not to Mr. Finneran.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我会先查阅一下  然后决定那些警官能看\N{\fs12}I'll review them first and then decide which of these files the police can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,社区服务部门尝试将布兰登·福特的儿子从家中带走\N{\fs12}Social Services is attempting to pull Brandon Ford's son from his home
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这一做法  毫无根据\N{\fs12}based on unfounded allegations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,法官大人  这些指控足以证明逮捕是正当的\N{\fs12}Your Honor, the allegations were substantial enough to justify an arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.03,0:10:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,布兰登·福特没有任何不法行为\N{\fs12}Brandon Ford is innocent of any wrongdoing,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我们相信这项指控将在即将举行的\N{\fs12}and we believe the charges will be dismissed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,初步听证会上被驳回\N{\fs12}at the upcoming preliminary hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们所要求的是把安德鲁送到寄养中心\N{\fs12}All we're asking is that Andrew be placed in foster care
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,直到对他父亲的指控得到解决\N{\fs12}until the charges against his father are resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,法官大人  安德鲁想要回家\N{\fs12}Your Honor, Andrew wants to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,情况属实吗  法林先生\N{\fs12}ls that true, Mr. Fallin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你的建议是什么\N{\fs12}And what is your recommendation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,福特先生要么离开家  同意接受监督探视\N{\fs12}Either Mr. Ford should leave the home and agree to supervised visits
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,要么把安德鲁送去寄养中心\N{\fs12}or Andrew should be placed in foster care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,法官大人  我能冒昧说一句吗\N{\fs12}Your Honor, may I speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有伤害我儿子\N{\fs12}I didn't hurt my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我被指责了一些  我永远都不会去做的事情\N{\fs12}I'm being blamed for something I would never do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我去哪都会有报纸报道这件事情\N{\fs12}Everywhere I go, newspapers are writing about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,人们会打电话到我家并且威胁我\N{\fs12}People are calling my house and threatening me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱我的儿子  而且我想照顾他\N{\fs12}And I love my son, and I want to take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我并没有做这件事情\N{\fs12}And I didn't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有做\N{\fs12}I did not do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,安德鲁将住在寄养中心  直到刑事指控得到解决\N{\fs12}Andrew will live in foster care until the criminal charges are resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.11,0:11:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你们有安排吗  索尔特女士\N{\fs12}Do you have a placement, Ms. Solt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有  谢谢你法官大人\N{\fs12}We do, Your Honor. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧\N{\fs12}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的\N{\fs12}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要一点咖啡吗\N{\fs12}Do you want some coffee?
