Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.13,0:12:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克\N{\fs12}Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚接到地方检察官办公室关于福特案子的电话\N{\fs12}I just got a call from the District Attorney's office about the Ford case.
