Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,否则法官会驳回这个案子的\N{\fs12}Otherwise the judge is gonna throw the case out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.94,0:13:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的  我会跟安德鲁谈谈的  - 好\N{\fs12}- All right. I'll talk to Andrew. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.38,0:13:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿尔文  - 劳里\N{\fs12}- Alvin. - Hey, Laurie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我想有空和你谈谈  - 当然可以\N{\fs12}- I'd like to talk to you sometime. - Of course.
