Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你有空吗\N{\fs12}You have a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有  进来吧\N{\fs12}Yeah, come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,地方检察官的理论是  在城市里到处开枪射击的人\N{\fs12}The DA has a theory that the person going around the city shooting people
