Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\fs12}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.07,0:13:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是他传唤我们以前的客户的原因\N{\fs12}That's why he subpoenaed the records of our former clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  好的\N{\fs12}Oh. Okay.
