Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这是对受虐儿童反应的扭曲\N{\fs12}This is a distortion of how an abused child reacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.33,0:13:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这是毫无根据  颠倒黑白的\N{\fs12}It's unfounded and it's invasive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吧  法官怎么说  - 那法官是个弱智\N{\fs12}- Well, what does the judge say? - The judge is an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.98,0:13:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,她对虐待儿童问题毫无经验\N{\fs12}She has no expertise regarding child abuse issues,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,没有对复杂事物的理解\N{\fs12}no understanding of the intricacies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但是艾尔文  如果法官命令我们交出文件的话\N{\fs12}But, Alvin, if the judge ordered us to hand over the files--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是政治迫害  露露  - 那我们就把文件交出来\N{\fs12}- It's a witch hunt, Lulu. - Then we hand over the files.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,交出这些记录是对受害者的惩罚\N{\fs12}Handing over these records punishes people for being victimized.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 艾尔文  - 你看  这些男性中的一个是前职业运动员\N{\fs12}- Alvin-- - Look, one of these men
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,前职业运动员\N{\fs12}is a former professional athlete
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他从来没有把自己的遭遇公之于众\N{\fs12}who never went public with what happened to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,另外一个男性被他父亲严重虐待过\N{\fs12}Another is a man who was so badly abused by his father
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他最后脑部受伤了\N{\fs12}that he ended up with a brain injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  我没打断什么吧\N{\fs12}Oh, I'm sorry. Was I interrupting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没有没有  怎么了\N{\fs12}No, no. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道那个孩子吧  他爸爸因为刺伤他被起诉\N{\fs12}You know the kid whose father was charged with stabbing him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 知道  安德鲁·福特  - 对\N{\fs12}- Yeah. Andrew Ford. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,对他爸爸不利的证据被推翻了\N{\fs12}The evidence against his father has been thrown out,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所以地方检察官希望安德鲁作证\N{\fs12}so the DA wants Andrew to testify.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,所以问题所在是什么\N{\fs12}So what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,安德鲁撒谎了\N{\fs12}Andrew's gonna lie on the stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  你认为你该指控他证词的真实性吗吗\N{\fs12}Well, do you think you should challenge his competency?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  如果成了的话  他就直接回他爸爸那里了\N{\fs12}Well, if that works then he's straight back with his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  你认为他爸爸袭击他了吗\N{\fs12}Right. And you think that his father attacked him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得袭击了\N{\fs12}Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,露露  我一个小时之内  就得提交这些资料\N{\fs12}Lulu, I gotta hand these papers over in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,艾尔文  我们没有根据对法官的判决提出上诉\N{\fs12}Alvin, we do not have the resources to appeal the judge's decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在强迫我吗\N{\fs12}Are you forcing me to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的  如果这样能让你感觉好一点  那么是的\N{\fs12}You know, if it makes you feel better, then, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,请交出这些文件\N{\fs12}I'm ordering you to hand over the files.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.43,0:14:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs12}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,宝宝刚踢了我一下\N{\fs12}The baby just kicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  阿尔文\N{\fs12}Hey, Alvin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,法官那边儿怎么样\N{\fs12}How did it go with the judge?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:14:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我得上交那些才叫了\N{\fs12}I have to hand over the records.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:15:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以帮你找\N{\fs12}I could help you look for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,看你能不能找到查尔斯·兰伯特和威廉·亨森\N{\fs12}See if you can find Charles Lambert and William Henson.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不是有一个橄榄球运动员叫查尔斯·兰伯特吗\N{\fs12}Wasn't there a football player named Charles Lambert?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个很大只的人  我记得大  他很壮\N{\fs12}He was a big guy. I remember him. He's huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.87,0:15:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这是其他两个文件\N{\fs12}Here are those other two files.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰·罗斯\N{\fs12}John Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,被他叔叔强暴了\N{\fs12}Raped by his uncle
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,然后在我安置他的第一个集体之家里  被一个比他大的男孩猥亵\N{\fs12}and then molested by an older boy in the first group home I placed him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白提起这个  是对警察有什么帮助\N{\fs12}I don't see how bringing this up helps the police at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我把亨森准备好\N{\fs12}I'll get the Henson file ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.96,0:15:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我叔叔他迫使我\N{\fs12}My uncle, he made me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我叔叔让我做这些事情\N{\fs12}My uncle made me do those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.49,0:15:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他告诉我  我必须这么做\N{\fs12}He told me I had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他告诉我如果我不的话  我会有麻烦\N{\fs12}He told me I was in trouble if I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是说  我叔叔对我做了什么\N{\fs12}I'm not saying that what my uncle did to me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没有改变我的生活\N{\fs12}didn't change my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我已经处理好了\N{\fs12}But I dealt with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我叔叔有问题  而且他从来不接受\N{\fs12}My uncle had a problem, and he never came to terms with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他  呃\N{\fs12}He, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.48,0:16:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他死的时候都没承认他做过什么\N{\fs12}He died without ever admitting what he'd done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但是那是他需要背负的罪孽  不是我的\N{\fs12}But that's his cross to bear, it's not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.98,0:16:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰\N{\fs12}John...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.47,0:16:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的政策是在  必须披露机密信息时  要通知客户\N{\fs12}It's our policy to inform people when we must reveal confidential information.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,马斯特森先生  我不活在过去\N{\fs12}Mr. Masterson, I don't live in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以如果告诉我这些会帮助警方办案\N{\fs12}So if talking to me about this will help the police solve a crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我意思是  我明白的\N{\fs12}I mean... I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  不要感到害怕  或者你必须和警察谈谈这件事。\N{\fs12}Well, don't feel intimidated or that you have to talk to the police about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.27,0:16:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我的家庭支持着我并且理解\N{\fs12}My family supports me and understands...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝看穿我们的一切\N{\fs12}and God sees us through.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你有一个美好的家庭\N{\fs12}You have a beautiful family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴你过的这么好\N{\fs12}It's good to see you doing so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.17,0:16:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  或许你想留下来一起吃晚饭\N{\fs12}Um, maybe you'd like to stay for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:16:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行  还有其他人我需要去通知\N{\fs12}I can't. I have other people I need to talk to about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起打扰了\N{\fs12}I'm sorry for the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,过去是\N{\fs12}The past is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起打扰了\N{\fs12}I'm sorry for the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你会给我们团队里的人说这件事吗\N{\fs12}You gonna tell the guys on my team about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能告诉任何人\N{\fs12}You can't tell nobody about what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.22,0:17:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  查尔斯  这超出我的控制了\N{\fs12}I'm sorry, Charles. It's out of my control.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会给任何人说的  艾尔文  永远不\N{\fs12}I never told nobody about this, Alvin. Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.74,0:17:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\fs12}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一个和我一样的人  - 当然了\N{\fs12}- A guy in my position. - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我有些新进展  这个地方不错\N{\fs12}-I got a good thing going here. This place is going good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我能看见\N{\fs12}I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是得到了一些支持  当地的  但是他们付钱\N{\fs12}I still got some endorsements. Local, but they pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能让人们知道我继父对我做了什么\N{\fs12}I can't have people knowing what my step-dad did to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs12}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我需要一个律师  - 他们有记录的\N{\fs12}- I'm gonna get a lawyer. - They have the records.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你应该合作  把它解决掉\N{\fs12}Maybe you should just cooperate and get it over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿尔文  - 查尔斯  宝贝\N{\fs12}- Alvin-- - Hey, Charles, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.98,0:17:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我能跟你说两句吗\N{\fs12}Can I talk to you for a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝\N{\fs12}Hey, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们 一个小时就能找到承办人了\N{\fs12}We've got the caterers in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这是谁\N{\fs12}Um...who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就是\N{\fs12}Uh...just, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  就是\N{\fs12}Well, just, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,先生你想要把这个给谁\N{\fs12}Who did you want this made out to, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿尔文  - 阿尔文\N{\fs12}- Alvin. - Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个大粉丝\N{\fs12}I'm a huge fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.48,0:18:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢你  - 谢谢\N{\fs12}- Thank you. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  伴郎们  他们需要测量一下尺寸\N{\fs12}Okay, the groomsmen, they need to get their measurements in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,查尔斯   你能着手去办吗\N{\fs12}Charles, will you get on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-  好的  - 好样的\N{\fs12}- Yes. - Okay, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我用轻木做的\N{\fs12}I made it out of balsa wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,手工室有多余的轻木\N{\fs12}There was extra balsa wood in the craft room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.04,0:18:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只是想把这些扔出去\N{\fs12}They were just gonna throw it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你说你喜欢船\N{\fs12}And you said you liked boats.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我意思是你是喜欢船的  对吧\N{\fs12}l--l mean, you did like boats, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你有阵子有辆摩托艇\N{\fs12}You had a motorboat for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  它在离这不远的码头里\N{\fs12}I did. Kept it in the marina not far from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,对 我记得\N{\fs12}Yeah, I remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.51,0:18:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,比利  我来这儿的原因\N{\fs12}So Billy, the reason I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.29,0:19:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你想要一个苹果吗  - 一个苹果\N{\fs12}- You want an apple? - An apple?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我有些苹果\N{\fs12}I got some apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,比利  今天警察来我办公室了\N{\fs12}Billy, the police came to my office today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我有麻烦了吗  - 没有\N{\fs12}- Am I in trouble? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我做什么了吗  - 没  比利  不是\N{\fs12}- Did I do something? - No, Billy. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那  那为什么警方因为我见你\N{\fs12}How--how come the police came to see you about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想要你的档案\N{\fs12}They want your records.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.02,0:19:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我  我不知道这什么意思\N{\fs12}I--I don't know what that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想知道你身上发生过什么\N{\fs12}They want to know about what happened to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,当你还是个男孩的时候  和你爸爸\N{\fs12}when you were a boy, with your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以呢\N{\fs12}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,比利  重点他们会和你聊聊发生了什么\N{\fs12}Billy, the point is they're gonna talk to you about what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想知道所有的细节\N{\fs12}They're gonna know all the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.79,0:19:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了什么吗\N{\fs12}Did I do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这关乎那些被杀的男性\N{\fs12}It's about all these men who have been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,男性被杀了吗\N{\fs12}Men are getting killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就在城里  新闻上都是\N{\fs12}ln the city. It's been in the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:20:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,所以比利\N{\fs12}So Billy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你有工作吗\N{\fs12}Do you have a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.08,0:20:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还酗酒吗  - 你呢\N{\fs12}- Still drinking? - You?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你老是闻起来像苏格兰威士忌\N{\fs12}You always smelled like scotch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.76,0:20:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,比利  不\N{\fs12}Ah, Billy, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我再也没喝过酒\N{\fs12}l, uh... I don't drink anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.14,0:20:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那很好啊  这对你好\N{\fs12}That's good. That's good for you.
