Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.82,0:28:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我是这么说的  但是比利并没有要求见我\N{\fs12}Yeah, I said I was, but Billy didn't ask for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.48,0:28:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,就是\N{\fs12}It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.36,0:28:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  很明显警察他做了这些事\N{\fs12}I mean, clearly the police think that he's doing these--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.95,0:28:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不   他们逮捕他的理由是流放  而不是谋杀\N{\fs12}No. They arrested him for an outstanding vagrancy warrant, not for the killings.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.96,0:28:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他们为什么这样做啊\N{\fs12}Why would they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.56,0:28:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想就这些枪击事件审问他\N{\fs12}They want to interrogate him about these shootings,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.25,0:29:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他们试图恐吓他\N{\fs12}and they're trying to intimidate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.20,0:29:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我看了他的文件\N{\fs12}I read his files.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.18,0:29:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs12}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.46,0:29:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他爸爸对他做的事情\N{\fs12}Things his father did to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.66,0:29:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这可能是是他做的吗\N{\fs12}You think he could be doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.26,0:29:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,比利  不可能\N{\fs12}Billy? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.62,0:29:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs12}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.88,0:29:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.58,0:29:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,警方逮捕了一个与最近枪击案有关\N{\fs12}Police have arrested a 29-year-old man
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.59,0:29:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,的29岁男性\N{\fs12}in relation to the recent shootings.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.00,0:29:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉·海森  一个从南边来的杂工\N{\fs12}William Henson, a handyman from the South Side,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.37,0:29:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,警方给他看了未执行的逮捕证之后\N{\fs12}confessed to the killings late last night
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.13,0:29:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他对对昨晚的谋杀供认不讳\N{\fs12}after police brought him in on an outstanding warrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.23,0:29:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,其他新闻  有更严重的火灾警报\N{\fs12}ln other news, a greater alarm fire
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.93,0:29:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,在南边  火警部门持续忙碌\N{\fs12}on the South Side kept fire departments busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.18,0:29:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,就这些\N{\fs12}So this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.43,0:29:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你会去证人席就坐\N{\fs12}You'll be seated on the witness stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.62,0:30:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,地方检察官会问你问题\N{\fs12}The District Attorney will be asking you questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.45,0:30:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他会问什么样的问题\N{\fs12}What kind of questions is he gonna ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.94,0:30:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他会问你对那晚还记得什么\N{\fs12}He's gonna ask you what you remember about the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.58,0:30:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我什么都不记得\N{\fs12}But I don't remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.53,0:30:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,地方检察官不会信的\N{\fs12}The District Attorney is not gonna believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.23,0:30:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,给你做检查的精神科医生也不会相信的\N{\fs12}And the psychiatrist that examined you doesn't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.47,0:30:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还会问我什么问题\N{\fs12}What other questions are they gonna ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.56,0:30:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你那天干什么了  你晚饭吃了什么\N{\fs12}What you did that day. What you had for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.57,0:30:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么时候上床睡觉了\N{\fs12}What time you went to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.97,0:30:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.11,0:30:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你记得什么吗\N{\fs12}Do you remember any of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.35,0:30:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们吃了通心粉的奶酪\N{\fs12}We had macaroni and cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.81,0:30:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我去做作业了  然后我睡觉了\N{\fs12}I did my homework and I went to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.06,0:30:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他想知道为什么你记得所有事情\N{\fs12}So he'll want to know why you can remember all of that
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.35,0:30:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,却不记得被袭击了\N{\fs12}but you can't remember being attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.28,0:30:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,安德鲁  在法庭外撒谎是一回事\N{\fs12}Andrew, it's one thing to lie outside of the courtroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.66,0:30:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,在席位上撒谎是另外一回事\N{\fs12}It's another thing to lie on the stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.82,0:30:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我在撒谎吗\N{\fs12}You think I'm lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.20,0:30:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你在撒谎\N{\fs12}I know you're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.44,0:30:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是希望你没有\N{\fs12}I just wish you wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.32,0:30:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有撒谎\N{\fs12}I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.68,0:30:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你记得那晚你吃了通心粉和奶酪\N{\fs12}But you remember you had macaroni and cheese for dinner that night?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.87,0:30:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.04,0:31:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你在你的卧室做了作业\N{\fs12}And that you did your homework in your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.56,0:31:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.87,0:31:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,十点你去睡觉了\N{\fs12}That you went to bed at 10:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.94,0:31:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.18,0:31:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,然后接下来发生的事情你不记得了\N{\fs12}And you just don't remember what happened next.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.77,0:31:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我醒来就在医院了\N{\fs12}I woke up in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.53,0:31:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定你不记得在你去医院之前发生了什么吗\N{\fs12}You sure you don't remember what happened before you got to the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.83,0:31:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我不记得了\N{\fs12}I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.21,0:31:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,安德鲁  你记得你的手和胳膊是怎么受伤的吗\N{\fs12}Andrew, do you remember how you got those cuts on your hands and arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.14,0:31:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不记得\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.32,0:31:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你不记得和谁在你卧室打起来了吗\N{\fs12}You don't remember fighting someone om in your bedroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.98,0:31:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我不记得\N{\fs12}I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.05,0:31:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你的你告诉警察有人在你的房间吗\N{\fs12}You remember telling the police about someone being in your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.74,0:31:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不记得  - 康诺利先生\N{\fs12}- No. - Mr. Connolly!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.68,0:31:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,当你采访这个证人时\N{\fs12}When you interviewed this witness,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.21,0:31:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他指认被告是攻击他的人吗\N{\fs12}did he name the defendant as his attacker?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.07,0:31:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.09,0:31:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在你希望他会在证人席上说出他的名字\N{\fs12}But now you're hoping he'll suddenly name him on the witness stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.38,0:31:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他告诉警察有一个男性在他卧室袭击他了\N{\fs12}He told the police that a man attacked him in his bedroom
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.87,0:31:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,而且那个袭击者告诉他不要告诉任何人\N{\fs12}and that the attacker told him not to tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.69,0:31:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,安德鲁  你说这些了吗\N{\fs12}Andrew, did you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.91,0:31:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我不记得\N{\fs12}I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.16,0:32:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  安德鲁  你可以下去了\N{\fs12}Thank you, Andrew. You can step down.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.88,0:32:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要撤销这些指控\N{\fs12}I'm dismissing these charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.06,0:32:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不是现在\N{\fs12}Not now, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.62,0:32:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我现在能回家了吗\N{\fs12}So I can go home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.97,0:32:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.72,0:32:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,安德鲁  我们什么都做不了  除非你帮我们\N{\fs12}Andrew, there's nothing more we can do to help you unless you help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.82,0:32:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗\N{\fs12}All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.25,0:32:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你需要什么打电话给我\N{\fs12}Call me if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.72,0:32:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很高兴孩子回来了  这是我一生中最美好的一天  真的\N{\fs12}We're thrilled to have our kid back. It's just the best day of my life, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.00,0:32:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰\N{\fs12}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.57,0:32:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,把武器放下\N{\fs12}Put the weapon down!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.86,0:32:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,别开枪  别拿枪对着他\N{\fs12}Don't shoot him! Don't shoot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.71,0:33:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,放下手里的武器\N{\fs12}Drop the weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.02,0:33:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰  放下它  约翰\N{\fs12}John! Put it down, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.00,0:33:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你了  约翰  把枪放下\N{\fs12}Please, John. Put the gun down.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.90,0:33:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你了  约翰  约翰  不要 不要这样  约翰\N{\fs12}Oh, please, John! John! Don't--don't do that, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.26,0:33:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰  约翰  我能帮你\N{\fs12}John. John, I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.11,0:33:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来帮你\N{\fs12}Let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.57,0:33:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不  -  拜托让我帮你吧\N{\fs12}- No. - Please let me help.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.71,0:33:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这些都无所谓了  马斯特森先生\N{\fs12}It doesn't matter any more, Mr. Masterson.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.85,0:33:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰  你有可爱的孩子  妻子  你不能\N{\fs12}John, you have a beautiful child, a wife. You can't--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.71,0:33:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这些都不重要了\N{\fs12}It doesn't matter any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.56,0:33:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰\N{\fs12}John.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.59,0:33:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿尔文  我们太担心了  - 我没事\N{\fs12}- Oh, Alvin, we were so worried. - I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.73,0:34:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,警方有好多问题  但是我没事\N{\fs12}Police had a bunch of questions, but I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.03,0:34:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  为什么不回家休息一会儿\N{\fs12}Well, why don't you go home and get some rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.31,0:34:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这都能得到照应\N{\fs12}We've got everything covered here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.65,0:34:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我没事  露露  - 你确定\N{\fs12}- I'm all right, Lulu. - Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.70,0:34:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我无敌的很\N{\fs12}I'm invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.50,0:34:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 艾尔文  - 有任何关于安德鲁·福特的消息吗\N{\fs12}- Alvin. - Any news on Andrew Ford?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.83,0:34:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.01,0:34:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我听警察局说了这件事\N{\fs12}Well, I heard about it at the police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.71,0:34:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他们派了很多人去找他\N{\fs12}They've got a lot of people out looking for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.28,0:34:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文\N{\fs12}Yeah. Alvin, wh--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.36,0:34:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.89,0:34:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么想的\N{\fs12}What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.16,0:34:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我怎么想的  - 对\N{\fs12}- What was I thinking? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.98,0:34:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得呢\N{\fs12}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.02,0:34:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,守灵怎么样\N{\fs12}How was the wake?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.13,0:34:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好难过\N{\fs12}It was sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.76,0:34:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,鉴于现在所有出来的消息  我是说\N{\fs12}And given everything that's come out since, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.61,0:34:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,人们不知道会怎么想格雷厄姆先生\N{\fs12}People just don't know what to think about Mr. Graham,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.37,0:34:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他们说凶手是热心市民\N{\fs12}now that they're saying his killer was a vigilante.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.64,0:34:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.98,0:34:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是痛恨在小肯身上发生的事\N{\fs12}I just hate to think that's what happened to Ken, Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.71,0:34:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但我干这行太久了  不会错过细节的\N{\fs12}But I've been in this business too long to miss the signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.68,0:34:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  小肯是个典型的虐待儿童的案例\N{\fs12}I mean, Ken, Jr. was a textbook case of child abuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.50,0:34:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思\N{\fs12}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.03,0:35:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,毒品   辍学  搬家\N{\fs12}Well, the drugs, the failing out of school, the moving around.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.51,0:35:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你不认为是他自己选择去做这些事的吗\N{\fs12}But don't you think he... chose to do those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.90,0:35:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认为\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.02,0:35:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但你是通过一个人如何受害来定义他的生活的\N{\fs12}But you're defining someone's life by how they were victimized.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.12,0:35:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,受害者喜欢这些  这会改变人的\N{\fs12}Being victimized like that, it changes people.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.46,0:35:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这改变了他们\N{\fs12}It changes them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.47,0:35:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,如果钱不是问题\N{\fs12}lf money were no object--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.51,0:35:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.11,0:35:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,如果钱不是问题  你想去哪工作\N{\fs12}lf money were no object, where would you work?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.36,0:35:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,在这儿还是法林&法林律所\N{\fs12}Here or at Fallin & Fallin?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.86,0:35:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,法林&法林律所\N{\fs12}Fallin & Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.27,0:35:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,或者就这里\N{\fs12}Or maybe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.28,0:35:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\fs12}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.65,0:35:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这地方很重要\N{\fs12}Well, this place matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.11,0:35:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上客户需要他们  人们在这真的为客户做了些好事\N{\fs12}People here do very good work for clients that actually need them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.73,0:36:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但是钱是个问题\N{\fs12}But money is an object.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.79,0:36:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,安德鲁\N{\fs12}Andrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.20,0:36:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪了\N{\fs12}Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.49,0:36:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得\N{\fs12}I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.70,0:36:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,有个孩子  特洛伊\N{\fs12}There's this kid, Troy,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.09,0:36:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,住在我家街上\N{\fs12}who lives down my street.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.81,0:36:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.15,0:36:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他在高中里\N{\fs12}He's in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.94,0:36:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我和他弟弟戴夫是朋友\N{\fs12}I'm friends with his little brother Dave.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.66,0:36:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,安德鲁  你想让我打电话给你妈妈吗\N{\fs12}Andrew, do you want me to call your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.83,0:36:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,让我说完\N{\fs12}Let me finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.29,0:36:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那天夜里发生的\N{\fs12}The night it happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.82,0:36:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我和罗伊\N{\fs12}me...and Troy...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.56,0:36:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,还有戴夫\N{\fs12}and Dave
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.83,0:36:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,在我房间里玩电动游戏\N{\fs12}were playing video games in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.54,0:36:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我打败了特洛伊   连着六次\N{\fs12}And I beat Troy, like, six times in a row...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.75,0:36:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我很擅长玩那个游戏\N{\fs12}'cause I'm good at the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.67,0:37:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,特洛伊袭击了你\N{\fs12}Did Troy attack you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.47,0:37:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这个游戏\N{\fs12}Because of the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.58,0:37:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs12}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.60,0:37:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,晚些的时候特洛伊过来了\N{\fs12}Troy came over, later that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.27,0:37:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是\N{\fs12}I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.38,0:37:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我邀请他过来的\N{\fs12}I invited him over.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.96,0:37:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们又开始玩这个游戏了\N{\fs12}And we started playing the game again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.35,0:37:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我让他赢了\N{\fs12}And I let him win.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.62,0:37:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我告诉他  我们可以一起做些别的\N{\fs12}And I told him we could do some other stuff...together.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.80,0:37:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.40,0:37:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们做了\N{\fs12}And we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.10,0:37:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.82,0:37:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,然后特洛伊\N{\fs12}And Troy...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.16,0:37:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,之后\N{\fs12}after...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.10,0:37:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,特洛伊真的生气了\N{\fs12}Troy was really mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.18,0:38:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他说这些以后都不会发生了\N{\fs12}He said it never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.22,0:38:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他是真的生气了\N{\fs12}He was really mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.75,0:38:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,特洛伊不想我告诉我任何人\N{\fs12}Troy didn't want me to tell anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.14,0:38:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿尔文在他办公室吗  - 是的\N{\fs12}- Is Alvin in his office?- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.24,0:38:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,比利  谢谢花的事儿\N{\fs12}Billy, thanks for the flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.44,0:38:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是些旧木头\N{\fs12}It was just some old wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.99,0:38:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.97,0:39:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我过来收尾\N{\fs12}I came to finish up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.68,0:39:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这工作收费多少\N{\fs12}What's the job pay again?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.57,0:39:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,每年$31,000  加上福利\N{\fs12}$31,000 annually, plus benefits.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.13,0:39:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一年需要接多少案子\N{\fs12}And how many cases would I have to take a year?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.88,0:39:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,大概300-400起案子\N{\fs12}Probably 300-400.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.80,0:39:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算什么时候休产假\N{\fs12}And what's your plan for when you take maternity leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.91,0:39:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话  我不知道\N{\fs12}Uh, honestly, I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.57,0:39:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来不太好  是吗\N{\fs12}Doesn't sound too good, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.37,0:39:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是不太好\N{\fs12}It doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.95,0:39:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我接受这份工作\N{\fs12}I'll take the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.41,0:39:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我和查尔斯谈过了\N{\fs12}I talked to Charles.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.14,0:40:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他和他未婚妻说过了  他说进展的都还不错\N{\fs12}He said he told his fiancée. He said it went all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.56,0:40:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你们  呃\N{\fs12}You guys, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.48,0:40:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你们说了很多\N{\fs12}You guys talk a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.95,0:40:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会聊\N{\fs12}We talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.73,0:40:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么告诉警方是你干的\N{\fs12}Why did you tell the police you did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.95,0:40:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  他们一直在说我做了  或者是我  我想做\N{\fs12}Well, they kept saying I did it or l--l wanted to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.44,0:40:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道怎么了吗  阿尔文\N{\fs12}And you know what, Alvin?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.68,0:40:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我想是我杀了这些人\N{\fs12}I kinda wish I did kill those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.11,0:40:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望是我做的\N{\fs12}I wish I did.
